structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
ORGANIZATION AND GOVERNMENT OF CITIES OF THE FIRST CLASS

law.catch_line: Public wharves and landings -- Control -- Charges.

text.section: The wharves and landings of cities of the first class shall be under the care and control of the Department of Public Works.
The department shall fix and receive reasonable charges for the use of the wharves and landings and shall keep them in order.

law.history: Amended 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 55, sec. 12. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 2860-1.
